    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2384190/extras/0ca3e6c6cbd4e0f5b2c85346f818b9f1.avif?t=1739142602\" width=620 height=122 /></span><br>Brave Bubble Heart is an arcade with a subtle roguelike inspiration, where you control a brave soul in the form of a bubble. Explore the randomly generated water abyss. Solve puzzles for useful rewards and defeat the creatures that will do anything to keep you trapped until death.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Satisfying combat.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2384190/extras/564625390f55fa9a4672797655de3b84.poster.avif?t=1739142602\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2384190/extras/564625390f55fa9a4672797655de3b84.webm?t=1739142602\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2384190/extras/564625390f55fa9a4672797655de3b84.mp4?t=1739142602\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>Fun puzzles.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2384190/extras/3eb755d30daa1cc0cb8f512a3797fa85.poster.avif?t=1739142602\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2384190/extras/3eb755d30daa1cc0cb8f512a3797fa85.webm?t=1739142602\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2384190/extras/3eb755d30daa1cc0cb8f512a3797fa85.mp4?t=1739142602\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>Save the prisoners from this dark place.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https